    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.F_SSTParcelByOrder
GO

IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.T_SSTParcelByOrder') )

GO

	[lms_parcelbyorder_aggrweight] numeric(28,2),

	[lms_parcelbyorder_aggrnoparcels] bigint,
	[lms_parcelbyorder_aggrweightexclspecdel] numeric(28,2),
	[lms_parcelbyorder_aggrchargeweightexclspecdel] numeric(28,2),
	[lms_parcelbyorder_aggrvolweightexclspecdel] numeric(28,2),
	[lms_parcelbyorder_aggrvolumiserweightexclspecdel] numeric(28,2),
	[lms_parcelbyorder_aggrmaxweightexclspecdel] numeric(28,2),
	[lms_parcelbyorder_aggrnoparcelsexclspecdel] bigint

GO
